e.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON string to deserialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">An instance of the specified type.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The target type.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.DeserializeFromFile``1(System.String,System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.DeserializeFromFile``1(System.String,System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_JsonNativeAot_DeserializeFromFile__1_System_String_System_String_'>DeserializeFromFile&lt;T&gt;(string, string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/JsonNativeAot.cs#L134'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Deserializes a JSON file into an object.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static T DeserializeFromFile&lt;T&gt;(string fileName, string relativePath) where T : IJsonSerializable, IJsonDesSerializable&lt;T&gt;, new()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>fileName</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The name of the file (without .json extension).</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>relativePath</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The relative path where the file is located.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">An instance of the specified type.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The target type.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.ParseJsonToDictionary(System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.ParseJsonToDictionary(System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_JsonNativeAot_ParseJsonToDictionary_System_String_'>ParseJsonToDictionary(string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/JsonNativeAot.cs#L125'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Parses a JSON string into a dictionary of property names and their string values.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static Dictionary&lt;string, string&gt; ParseJsonToDictionary(string json)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>json</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON string to parse.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.dictionary-2'>Dictionary</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>, <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A dictionary containing property names as keys and their string representations as values.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Examples</h4><pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">string json = \"{\\\"Name\\\":\\\"John\\\",\\\"Age\\\":\\\"30\\\"}\";\nvar props = JsonNativeAot.ParseJsonToDictionary(json);\n// props[\"Name\"] = \"John\"\n// props[\"Age\"] = \"30\"</code></pre>\n<h4 class='section'>Remarks</h4><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This method provides low-level access to JSON parsing. It returns a raw dictionary\nof property names and values without deserializing to a specific type.\nComplex values (objects and arrays) are returned as raw JSON strings.\nTime Complexity: O(n) where n is the length of the JSON string.\nSpace Complexity: O(n) for the output dictionary.</p>\n<h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when json is null.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Exceptions.JsonParsingException.html'>JsonParsingException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when JSON parsing fails.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.Serialize``1(``0)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.Serialize``1(``0)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_JsonNativeAot_Serialize__1___0_'>Serialize&lt;T&gt;(T)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/JsonNativeAot.cs#L81'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Serializes an object to a JSON string.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static string Serialize&lt;T&gt;(T instance) where T : IJsonSerializable</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>instance</code> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The instance to serialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A JSON string representation of the object.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The type of the object to serialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.SerializeToFile``1(``0,System.String,System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.SerializeToFile``1(``0,System.String,System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_JsonNativeAot_SerializeToFile__1___0_System_String_System_String_'>SerializeToFile&lt;T&gt;(T, string, string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/JsonNativeAot.cs#L90'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Serializes an object to a JSON file.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static void SerializeToFile&lt;T&gt;(T instance, string fileName, string relativePath) where T : IJsonSerializable</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>instance</code> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The instance to serialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>fileName</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The name of the file (without .json extension).</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>relativePath</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The relative path where the file will be saved.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.JsonNativeAot.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The type of the object to serialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
